* Mon Jul 06 2008 Michael Stone <michael@laptop.org> - 0.6-1.olpc3
- Fix dependencies: crond -> cronie.

* Wed Jul 02 2008 Michael Stone <michael@laptop.org> - 0.5-1.olpc3
- Initial release of this spec.
